comments: Davis (LAL) places a resting hand on Jackson's (MEM) body as the contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Jackson (MEM) briefly places his hand to Davis' (LAL) side as he rolls towards the basket before releasing as the contact does not affect Davis' FOM.
Reaves (LAL) brings his hands toward Jackson (MEM) as the contact that occurs as Reaves (LAL) releases away to roll is marginal.
James (LAL) switches his pivot foot.
Jemison (MEM) legally contests Davis' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Hachimura (LAL) cleanly deflects the loose ball away from Jackson (MEM) during the rebound.
Jemison (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball, but continues forward into Davis (LAL) and dislodges him from his position.
Davis (LAL) gets drawn in the air towards LaRavia (MEM) and initiates contact to his body that affects the driving shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) engages and disengages with Jackson (MEM) as he rolls towards the basket after setting the pick.
Prince (LAL) gathers the ball on left foot and comes to a jump stop before releasing the pass.
James (LAL) lifts and re-plants his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Goodwin (MEM) releases from Davis (LAL) during the drive as he slightly extends his off-arm, which does not affect Davis' ability to defend.
Goodwin (MEM) maintains his pivot foot prior to the shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) legally contests Goodwin's (MEM) layup attempt.
Prince (LAL) establishes himself in Allen's (MEM) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
LaRavia (MEM) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
Jackson (MEM) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two steps before the driving shot attempt.
Hachimura (LAL) extends his leg into Jackson (MEM) and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (LAL) briefly grasps Goodwin's (MEM) jersey as he deflects the rebound.
Coach Jenkins (MEM) is assessed an unsportsmanlike technical foul.
Hachimura (LAL) legally contests LaRavia's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
